column16: Hanley Ramirez grounds out softly, third baseman Kyle Seager to first baseman Dae-Ho Lee.

Mookie Betts doubles (30) on a sharp ground ball to left fielder Guillermo Heredia.
Andrew Benintendi grounds out, second baseman Robinson Cano to first baseman Dae-Ho Lee.
Sandy Leon grounds out to first baseman Dae-Ho Lee.
Aaron Hill grounds out, second baseman Robinson Cano to first baseman Dae-Ho Lee.
Jordy Mercer grounds into a force out, third baseman Kyle Seager to second baseman Robinson Cano.   Erik Kratz out at 2nd.
Erik Kratz reaches on a fielding error by third baseman Kyle Seager.   Sean Rodriguez to 3rd.
Josh Harrison grounds out sharply, shortstop Ketel Marte to first baseman Adam Lind.

Tommy Pham grounds into a force out, third baseman Kyle Seager to second baseman Robinson Cano.   Eric Fryer out at 2nd.
Greg Garcia called out on strikes.
